Make sure you install the libgnugetopt port from
/usr/ports/devel/libgnugetopt because at current
this package is needed to compile TuxNES.

For those not using FreeBSD's port structure:

http://www.geocities.com/SiliconValley/Code/3502/libgnugetopt-1.1.tar.gz

NetBSD, at least from version 1.5 and onward, defines long support by
default.

